item.title: I have a big problem so would sum 1 plz help me ive been stuck for 2 days
item.dc:creator: @Tico135 Tico
item.description:
@Tico135 wrote:

Edit your environment variables.
My Computer>>View system information>>Advanced>>Environment Variables
Make a new variable, name it PATH. For the variable value put this: C:\Program Files\Java\jdk1.6.0_01\bin
Make a new variable, name it CLASSPATH. For the variable value put this: CLASSPATH=C:\Program Files\Java\jdk1.6.0_01\bin;%CLASSPATH%;
Click ‘Apply’ and then ‘ok’.
